    "description": "In the 1950s, the American vocal group the Platters was the only major act to appeal to teenagers and their parents in equal measure. They had planned it that way or, at least, their manager, Buck Ram, did.\u00a0 <br /><br /><div><br /></div><div><table style=\"color:rgb(84,84,84);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;\" width=\"700\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"20%\"><b>Artist</b></td><td width=\"30%\"><b>Song Title</b></td><td width=\"30%\"><b>Album</b></td><td width=\"10%\"><b>Label</b></td><td width=\"10%\"><b>Played</b></td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>Barry White</td><td>Walkin' In The Rain With The One I Love</td><td>White Gold</td><td>Island Def Jam</td><td>11:03 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>Harbor Lights</td><td>The Remasters</td><td>BELIEVE - Millennium Digital Remaster</td><td>11:07 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>Percy Faith</td><td>Theme From A Summer Place</td><td>US 1960 - March</td><td>ORCHARD - Top Twenty</td><td>11:08 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>Dinah Washington,Brook Benton</td><td>A Rockin' Good Way (To Mess Around And Fall In Love)</td><td>Greatest Duets</td><td>UMG - UMG Recordings, Inc.</td><td>11:09 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>The Platters</td><td>Bark Battle and Ball</td><td>The Hits of 1955, Vol. 2</td><td>Golden Bridge Records</td><td>11:13 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>Enchanted</td><td>The Platters : Only You and Their Best Songs Ever</td><td>BELIEVE - The Restoration Project</td><td>11:16 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>The Platters</td><td>Heaven on Earth</td><td>Yo Quiero Un Mambo</td><td>BELIEVE - Golden Bridge Records</td><td>11:19 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>Remember When</td><td>The Platters - Platinum Edition</td><td>BELIEVE - Platinum Masterpieces</td><td>11:21 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>The Platters</td><td>You'll Never Never Know</td><td>Universal Masters Collection</td><td>UMG - EMI</td><td>11:24 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>(By The) Sleepy Lagoon</td><td>The Collection 1956-1962</td><td>Universal Music</td><td>11:27 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>Jackie Gleason</td><td>Body and Soul</td><td>I'll Be Seeing You</td><td>BELIEVE - Gotcha!</td><td>11:29 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>It Isn't Right</td><td>The Magic Touch: An Anthology</td><td>UMG - Island Records</td><td>11:33 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>The Platters</td><td>It's Raining Outside</td><td>The Magic Touch: An Anthology</td><td>UMG - Island Records</td><td>11:35 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>My Dream</td><td>Cool</td><td>BELIEVE - The Restoration Project</td><td>11:38 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>The Platters</td><td>The Great Pretender</td><td>Jukebox-Hits (Vol. 3)</td><td>Old Style</td><td>11:47 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>The Platters</td><td>My Prayer</td><td>The Platters : Only You and Their Best Songs Ever</td><td>BELIEVE - The Restoration Project</td><td>11:50 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><td>Buchanan and Goodman</td><td>The Flying Saucer (Parts 1 & 2)</td><td>The Space Age Generation, Volume 10</td><td>Play Digital</td><td>11:53 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color:rgb(236,235,192);\"><td>Henry Mancini & His Orchestra</td><td>Johnny's Theme - (theme from the \"Tonight Show\")</td><td>Big Screen, Little Screen</td><td>SME - RCA Records Label</td><td>11:53 AM*</td></tr><tr style=\"background